data.description:
Half off first month's rent if tenant signs an 18 month lease! (Valid from 12/10/2023 till 01/31/2024)

Welcome to luxury living in the heart of Stone Oak, just a short commute from vibrant San Antonio! This executive-level property offers a refined and exclusive lifestyle in a prestigious gated neighborhood.

This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath home is designed for the discerning professional seeking comfort and sophistication. The property includes a dedicated office space, perfect for remote work or personal projects. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of a stone fireplace, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere.

The attention to detail is evident throughout, with custom features such as high ceilings and built-ins that add an extra layer of elegance. The kitchen boasts modern amenities and a layout that makes entertaining a breeze. The separate living/game room upstairs allows for even more options for entertaining.

Step outside to discover your private oasis a backyard adorned with a hot tub, a soothing fountain, and ample deck space for outdoor gatherings. Whether you're enjoying a quiet evening or entertaining guests, this outdoor space is a perfect retreat.

For those with an active lifestyle, the community offers amenities such as pickleball courts, tennis courts, and private pool. The combination of upscale living and recreational options makes this property an ideal choice for those who appreciate both luxury and leisure.

Experience the epitome of executive living in Stone Oak, where every detail has been meticulously crafted to enhance your lifestyle. Don't hesitate; apply today!

Owner is also willing to leave current furnishings to tenant for additional price if interested.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities and for maintaining the yard. Tenant is responsible for any HOA violations and fees associated. Refrigerator and hot tub are provided to tenant as a benefit. Owner is not responsible for maintenance or replacement of refrigerator or hot tub. 

Fees:

Application Fee of $25 per adult if prospective tenant applies through brunnerpm.com. Also welcome to apply through Zillow

Administrative fee of $65 due at lease signing

Animals:

Pet Fee of $25/month per household pet
Assistance animals $0 Pet Fee
All household pets and assistance animals must complete pet screening

Credit Scores:

Credit Scores will be averaged for all applicants:

Average score 650+: Deposit = 1 month's rent
Average score 600-649: Case by case decision
Average score under 599; denial of application

Income Requirements:

Income must be greater than 3 times the monthly rent.
Income must be verified through paystubs or employer offer letter.
Self employed applicants need to provide bank statements and/or tax returns.

Background:

Be prepared to upload your driver's license and paystubs as part of the application process. 
No felony convictions, bankruptcies, or evictions in the last 5 years. 

Rental/Mortgage History:

Two years of verified rental history or mortgage history.
No foreclosures within the last 5 years.
